577
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,120
so he's not your brother now.

578
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:38,800
We certainly can't go home with him.

579
00:24:38,800 --> 00:24:40,800
But Dad has already bought him a bed.

580
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:43,000
You've bought a bed for him already!

581
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:48,520
He Ziqiu.

582
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,680
Ziqiu.

583
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:58,600
He Ziqiu.

584
00:24:59,040 --> 00:25:00,800
Why did you come here?

585
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:02,090
I thought I said that

586
00:25:02,320 --> 00:25:04,240
I was going to stay in my grandma-in-law's house for several days

587
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:06,080
and would bring back some sticky corn cobs for you.

588
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:07,600
Why didn't you wait for me?

589
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,440
Ziqiu.

590
00:25:15,760 --> 00:25:16,320
Dad.

591
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:17,240
Hey.

592
00:25:21,600 --> 00:25:22,120
So,

593
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,260
you're going to...

594
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,400
I'll carry it for you.

595
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:31,120
Come on.

596
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:33,850
Look at this.

597
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:44,760
All rural kids

598
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:45,800
go to work

599
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:46,640
in the field.

600
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:49,280
Who would leave their kids idle?

601
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:51,800
What about

602
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:53,720
Ziqiu's school?

603
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:54,760
Who knows?

604
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:57,200
Just let him attend some free classes.

605
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,730
I don't have money for that.

606
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,970
If He Mei owes you money,

607
00:26:01,080 --> 00:26:02,240
go ask her for it.

608
00:26:04,320 --> 00:26:04,840
Ma'am,

609
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,320
we really aren't here to

610
00:26:06,320 --> 00:26:07,560
ask for money.

611
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,520
We just want to see Ziqiu.

612
00:26:12,280 --> 00:26:13,960
You're quite a sensible man.

613
00:26:14,320 --> 00:26:15,440
Why did He Mei

614
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:17,080
go to Shenzhen to work?

615
00:26:17,520 --> 00:26:18,760
It was her decision.

616
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:19,880
Anyway,

617
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:21,680
she went there alone.

618
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:23,360
Back then,

619
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,560
she insisted on

620
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:26,490
marrying that jerk Zhao Huaguang.

621
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:27,400
I disagreed,

622
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:29,280
but she wouldn't give up.

623
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,840
Now that she got married,

624
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:32,720
she could've just lived a normal life.

625
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:34,960
You get along with whoever you marry.

626
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:36,240
If it turns out to be a bad decision,

627
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,280
then blame fate.

628
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:37,880
Am I right?

629
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,290
How unexpected that

630
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:40,640
after a period

631
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,080
as short as one year,

632
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:44,160
she came back and said she got divorced.

633
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,620
And she was even pregnant.

634
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:48,000
I told her to have an abortion, but she wouldn't.

635
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,280
She said she would raise the child herself.

636
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:51,010
I went to talk to Zhao Huaguang,

637
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:52,480
but that jerk said that

638
00:26:52,800 --> 00:26:53,760
he didn't want the child

639
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:54,760
and that she should have an abortion immediately.

640
00:26:54,760 --> 00:26:55,360
Mom,

641
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,640
why do you talk about this again?

642
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:59,440
Why shouldn't I talk about this?

643
00:27:08,360 --> 00:27:09,520
Leave Ziqiu to me.

644
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:14,240
I'll bring him to the city

645
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,690
and support his schooling.

646
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:19,540
I'll raise him.

647
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,480
Ziqiu, have some meat.

648
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:07,520
Don't you love

649
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:08,780
sweet-and-sour ribs?

650
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:09,440
Dad,

651
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:10,960
I don't like meat.

652
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:13,240
I just like vegetables.

653
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:15,920
No!

654
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,120
You must eat meat in order to grow tall.

655
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:19,720
Trust me.

656
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:21,300
Thank you, Dad.

657
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:23,520
Have some.

658
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:30,000
Ziqiu,

659
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,690
has your mother sent the money?

660
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:34,840
Ziqiu,

661
00:28:35,120 --> 00:28:36,440
you've got to impress them.

662
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,200
If you don't behave,

663
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,730
your dad will send you away.

664
00:28:40,120 --> 00:28:41,560
Why did you scare him?

665
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:42,560
I was teasing him.

666
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:48,560
Please, don't tease a kid

667
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:49,400
like that.

668
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:53,060
He's just a kid, so it doesn't matter.

669
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,960
But a kid would take it to his heart.

670
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,600
Ziqiu,

671
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:01,720
don't cry. It's OK.

672
00:29:02,240 --> 00:29:03,160
It's OK, kid.

673
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:04,760
She was wrong.

674
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:07,240
I won't send you away.

675
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,080
I won't.

676
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,640
Oh, come on.

677
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:11,520
I was just teasing you.

678
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:13,180
You really took it seriously?

679
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:14,480
A boy shouldn't be so narrow-minded.

680
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,880
Just eat please.

681
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:19,320
If you still don't eat, the noodles will get soggy.

682
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:23,120
So funny!

683
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:25,520
Stop it.

684
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:27,600
Can't you see Haichao is upset?

685
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:29,580
Why so serious?

686
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:30,920
Trust me.

687
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:32,960
I won't send you away.

688
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:34,440
You're not going anywhere.

689
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,840
You'll just be around me.

690
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,080
Just like Jianjian,

691
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,560
you're my child.

692
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:42,380
How can a father send his son away?

693
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:44,680
Trust me.

694
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:46,240
I won't send you away.

695
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:49,520
My mother said that

696
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:51,480
you took my kid to your family

697
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:54,360
and allow him to study worry-free.

698
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,480
I can only say

699
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:57,840
thank you.

700
00:29:58,240 --> 00:30:00,560
Thank you for giving Ziqiu a father.

701
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,240
You're Ziqiu's lucky star.

702
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:05,640
Right now,

703
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:07,280
I'm having some difficulties.

704
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:08,480
I really can't deliver you the money

705
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:10,160
to cover his living expenses.

706
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:12,360
Please treat Ziqiu

707
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:14,240
as your own son.

708
00:30:15,080 --> 00:30:16,280
Don't worry.

709
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:17,640
Since you are the one who raises him,

710
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:19,040
he'll be your son.

711
00:30:19,040 --> 00:30:20,360
He'll treat you

712
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:22,080
as his real father,

713
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,560
because he's a good kid

714
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:25,280
who cares about bonds.

715
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,080
What a pity that

716
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:29,360
I have

717
00:30:29,360 --> 00:30:31,960
only this short period of mother-son relationship with him!

718
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,200
I have no luck to

719
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,000
continue being his mother.

720
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,940
But in this distant place,

721
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,400
I'll love him and bless him

722
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,600
in my heart,

723
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:42,760
forever.

724
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,400
I will manage to

725
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:47,800
repay you

726
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:49,440
the money I owe you one day.

727
00:30:50,560 --> 00:30:51,600
Sorry.

728
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:18,080
Today,

729
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:20,240
I said something I shouldn't have

730
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:21,560
and upset your father.

731
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:22,760
It's OK.

732
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,770
He won't take it seriously.

733
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:28,570
I do know that I've been bothering you,

734
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:29,280
but

735
00:31:29,280 --> 00:31:29,560
we...

736
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:30,690
It's for my own good.

737
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:31,840
I know.

738
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:38,080
It's still my fault for being incompetent.

739
00:31:38,080 --> 00:31:38,880
There you go again.

740
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:39,880
OK, OK, OK.

741
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,240
I won't talk about it.

742
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,320
Ziqiu.

743
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:46,040
Yes?

744
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:49,240
Promise me one thing.

745
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:50,240
What is it?

746
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:54,840
Forget your mother.

747
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:57,920
Stop asking around about her

748
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:00,360
and stop looking for her.

749
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:03,020
She has left for so many years.

750
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:06,720
Don't always cling to the things of your childhood.

751
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,520
This will be good for both of you.

752
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:13,240
I don't mean anything substantial.

753
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:15,120
I just want to know why.

754
00:32:18,360 --> 00:32:19,160
Ziqiu,

755
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:23,130
you should keep your good conscience.

756
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:26,090
Your dad has been so kind to you.

757
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:28,120
Don't hurt his feelings.

758
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:31,720
I know.

759
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,530
Good boy.

760
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,880
Happy birthday.

761
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:42,160
Thank you.

762
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,560
You can open it.

763
00:32:46,080 --> 00:32:46,600
OK.

764
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:55,480
A watch.

765
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,600
Thank you.

766
00:32:56,840 --> 00:32:58,040
You have a good taste.

767
00:32:58,360 --> 00:32:59,600
Let me help you put it on.

768
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:00,160
Thanks, but no need.

769
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:02,760
I can't wear a watch while playing basketball.

770
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:03,850
I'll put it here.

771
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:04,840
See you later.

772
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:11,890
Give me the ball.

773
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,480
Keep doing your homework.

774
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,340
Don't go slack.

775
00:34:05,360 --> 00:34:06,760
Stop knocking.

776
00:34:12,190 --> 00:34:13,480
Oh goodness.

777
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,360
What are you doing here

778
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:16,600
on such a weekend day?

779
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:17,730
Where's my brother?

780
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:18,920
He's not here.

781
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:21,080
He's not at home or the restaurant.

782
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:22,560
If he's not here, where can he be?

783
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:23,320
How do I know?

784
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:24,760
Call his cell phone.

785
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:25,600
I tried.

786
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,260
He left his cell phone at home.

787
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:29,400
Then I don't know all the more.

788
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,230
He should be back

789
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,040
very soon.

790
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,360
You can sit there

791
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,690
and wait for him. Don't get in the doorway.

792
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:36,800
What is it for?

793
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,199
Take me to my brother.

794
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,840
Why must I do that?

795
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:41,710
If you don't,

796
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:42,520
I won't leave.

797
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:44,120
Then stay here.

798
00:34:45,710 --> 00:34:46,909
Take me to my brother.

799
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:47,480
Let go!

800
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:48,840
Let go!

801
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,280
If you don't let go, I'll use violence.

802
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,120
I'll count from one to three.

803
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:51,560
One...

804
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:52,760
I'll pay you 100 yuan.

805
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:57,560
It's 100 yuan.

806
00:35:06,560 --> 00:35:08,040
You're just taking circles.

807
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,500
Is my brother really here?

808
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,890
I don't know either.

809
00:35:11,120 --> 00:35:12,120
It's just a guess.

810
00:35:12,520 --> 00:35:14,120
You'd better find him for me.

811
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:17,640
When are you people going to leave?

812
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:18,960
It's none of your business.

813
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,560
It's certainly my business.

814
00:35:20,560 --> 00:35:22,400
After you annoying people leave,

815
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:24,460
my brother will be mine exclusively.

816
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:25,320
My grandma said that

817
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,320
he's my brother.

818
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:27,800
He has no ties with you.

819
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,450
You two are just neighbors.

820
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,520
I don't care what you people say.

821
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:33,120
I'm with him all the time

822
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:34,000
anyway.

823
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:36,200
Humph.

824
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:36,760
Humph.

825
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:43,080
Oh yes, I remember.

826
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:45,360
He should be doing grocery shopping in the supermarket.

827
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:45,890
Let's go.

828
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,760
Follow up. Hurry.

829
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,960
You are fooling me.

830
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:56,250
Then don't come with me.

831
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:11,290
Where is she?

832
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,440
Hey.

833
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:17,060
It's OK. It'll be fine.

834
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:17,600
Don't worry.

835
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:18,360
I'm here.

836
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:22,960
Who is Qin Meiyang's family member?

837
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,240
I am. I'm her brother.

838
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:25,200
Look.

839
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:25,840
She has a fracture in her forearm

840
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:26,960
and some slight bruises on the head,

841
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,420
but these aren't serious.

842
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:29,160
Now, go inside

843
00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:29,600
with me

844
00:36:29,600 --> 00:36:30,520
and go through the admission procedure.

845
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:31,080
OK.

846
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,640
How did she fall over?

847
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,610
I don't know either.

848
00:36:39,720 --> 00:36:40,480
It's OK.

849
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:45,720
She's still so young,

850
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,640
and you took her to run around.

851
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:48,520
If anything serious had happened,

852
00:36:48,520 --> 00:36:49,480
who would take the responsibilities?

853
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,360
I will.

854
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:51,960
I'll cover the medical costs.

855
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:53,680
Is it just about the medical costs?

856
00:36:53,680 --> 00:36:54,200
Well,

857
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:57,640
I'm also so curious.

858
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:59,160
How did she fall over?

859
00:36:59,160 --> 00:37:00,240
Explain to me.

860
00:37:01,640 --> 00:37:02,400
I don't know.

861
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:03,520
You were with her,

862
00:37:03,520 --> 00:37:05,080
and you're telling me you don't know?

863
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:06,600
You think I can believe that?

864
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:07,360
I'll ask you again.

865
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,560
How did she fall over?

866
00:37:19,680 --> 00:37:20,680
Chengzi is awake.

867
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,000
How was it?

868
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:29,170
It's OK, Dad.

869
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,560
Go and take care of the restaurant.

870
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:31,240
I'm here.

871
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,240
Is Chengzi really OK?

872
00:37:33,520 --> 00:37:34,780
She's OK. Don't worry.

873
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,400
Don't worry about my mother.

874
00:37:39,320 --> 00:37:39,920
Hey,

875
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:41,400
um…

876
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:41,920
My brother!

877
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,240
I want him.

878
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:44,680
My brother!

879
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:46,320
I want him.

880
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:49,020
You can go home.

881
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:57,520
OK. Then let's go home.

882
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,200
I'll cook

883
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:01,580
and tell Ziqiu to bring some food for you.

884
00:38:01,600 --> 00:38:02,160
OK.

885
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:02,880
Go ahead.

886
00:38:10,200 --> 00:38:10,960
Let's go.

887
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:12,890
We're not welcome here.

888
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:25,960
I remember you used to

889
00:38:26,120 --> 00:38:27,680
like her very much.

890
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:29,440
When you were so young back then,

891
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:31,500
you already took care of your sister.

892
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:33,780
And she liked to be around you.

893
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,680
Whoever asked her,

894
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:36,920
she always answered she liked you best.

895
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:40,480
Probably because I always talked about you with her,

896
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:41,360
Chengzi liked you

897
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,440
when she saw you

898
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,440
for the first time.

899
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:46,920
Maybe to her,

900
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,160
besides her parents,

901
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:50,650
you're the closest family member.

902
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:52,280
So, when she saw you

903
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:54,610
being so nice to Li Jianjian, she would...

904
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:56,200
certainly feel jealous.

905
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,040
So,

906
00:39:00,120 --> 00:39:01,780
after all, she's your sister.

907
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,560
Can you

908
00:39:04,200 --> 00:39:05,520
share your affection for Li Jianjian,

909
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,520
even just a little bit,

910
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:07,720
with her?

911
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,000
Please?

912
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:14,520
I won't share

913
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:18,440
what belongs to Li Jianjian with other people.

914
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:19,320
I'm not you.

915
00:39:48,240 --> 00:39:49,640
I finished my shower, Li Jianjian.

916
00:39:49,640 --> 00:39:50,370
You go ahead.

917
00:39:51,560 --> 00:39:52,120
OK.

918
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,360
I'll go later.

919
00:39:54,160 --> 00:39:55,220
It's almost 11:00.

920
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:57,010
Just have a shower and go to bed.

921
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,200
Dad doesn't want you to eat candy.

922
00:40:08,200 --> 00:40:09,330
While he's not here,

923
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:10,580
eat it quickly.

924
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,080
Oh, you ignore me!

925
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:14,880
Just open your mouth.

926
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:16,880
Ah, ah, ah!

927
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:17,920
Good girl.

928
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:23,240
So?

929
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:24,400
You're still

930
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,880
thinking about that silly girl?

931
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,000
You didn't push her.

932
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,080
She fell over herself.

933
00:40:28,080 --> 00:40:29,080
Why should you be upset?

934
00:40:29,080 --> 00:40:29,940
Isn't it silly?

935
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,440
I'm not silly.

936
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,800
I know it wasn't my fault.

937
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:36,760
Then why are you so upset?

938
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,290
It was not you who fell over.

939
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:42,770
She's still a kid after all.

940
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:44,220
And she had a fracture.

941
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:47,280
These days,

942
00:40:47,640 --> 00:40:48,520
Ling Xiao has been frequenting the hospital

943
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,880
as soon as school was over

944
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,140
and even stayed there.

945
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,440
I haven't seen him for days.

946
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:56,040
He must be so upset.
